Description: Hi eBayers, Up for sale is a custom, “Fender” Bullet Stratocaster. It was made using a Squire Bullet Strat body, switching out the pick guard and nobs (for Fender parts) and adding DiMarzio pickups as well as that famous “Bullet” header on the truss rod. So, it’s a modified Squire made to look like a classic Fender Bullet Strat. I can’t recall what type of DiMarzio’s these are, but can state that they have a “crunchier” tone than the original pickups Squire provided. This is more of a rocker’s guitar. It’s been in storage for a few years, strings unwound, and is looking for a new home. All functions operate precisely as should, but it may need new strings. While you’re here, be sure to check out my other listings and feel free to ask any questions before making “the buy.” Be well and Happy eBaying! Purchase will include: 1xCustom Squire Bullet Stratocaster w/Tremolo Arm 1xFender Guitar Gig Bag
Title: Custom Squire (Fender) “Bullet” Stratocaster w/DiMarzio Pickups & Guitar Bag
